DATA:
Guess that did it... But...
Where am I now!?

I don't think you know what you've got yourself
into, Jamie... Leave... And never come back...
Somehow you'll find yoursel- hold on.

*GULP* *GULP* *GULP*
Man, I got the GOOD stuff today!
What do you mean, I'll find myself?

You said that somehow I'd 'find myself'?
Find myself where, here?
Oh my god, this shit hits hard!!!

Don't fucking judge me, I don't see YOU drinking
five gallons a day.

Actually, I don't think I've ever seen you
drink anything... Ever...
